months%20preparing%20for%20it%2C%20we%20didn't%20get%20it%20all%20right.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20services%20are%20back%20up%20and%20running%2C%20he%20said.%20But%20there%20are%20still%20some%20issues%20with%20call%20quality%20and%20reliability.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20our%20biggest%20priority%20and%20the%20full%20team%20is%20working%20around%20the%20clock%20to%20restore%20service%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20buzzy%20phone%20was%20launched%20in%20the%20fall%20of%202024%20and%20spread%20quickly%20through%20word%20of%20mouth%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20in%20Facebook%20groups%20focused%20on%20parenting.%20The%20phones%2C%20which%20are%20colorful%20and%20corded%2C%20cost%20%2475.%20It's%20free%20to%20call%20other%20Tin%20Can%20users%20(or%20you%20can%20pay%20%2410%20a%20month%20to%20call%20outside%20lines%2C%20similar%20to%20VoIP)%2C%20which%20is%20what%20makes%20the%20service%20so%20popular%20with%20parents%3A%20They%20can%20create%20a%20sort%20of%20Tin%20Can%20closed%20circuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Maria%20Pahuja%2C%20a%20parent%20in%20Richmond%2C%20Virginia%2C%20everything%20was%20working%20fine%20when%20she%20installed%20the%20Tin%20Can%20phone%20on%20Christmas%20Eve%20morning.%20%26quot%3BIt%20worked%20great%2C%20the%20kids%20were%20using%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThen%2C%20Christmas%20morning%2C%20it%20stopped%20working.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20you'd%20pick%20it%20up%2C%20and%20there%20would%20be%20a%20dial%20tone%2C%20you%20would%20call%2C%20and%20nothing%20would%20happen.%20Once%20in%20a%20while%2C%20a%20call%20would%20go%20through%2C%20and%20then%20two%20minutes%20later%20another%20call%20wouldn't%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20wasn't%20consistent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ddf39cd1-8bca-4dd2-8478-ca96cc522853%5C%22%3EWhy%20parents%20are%20loving%20the%20concept%20of%20the%20Tin%20Can%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20Conz%20Preti%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22h